Title: Jordana Lipstick 3.4(Raspberry)
Description: Jordana Lipsticks help keep your lips soft and supple, with beautiful, dazzling colors. These are rich and creamy and give soft shiny finish to your lips. The best part is these do not smudge off your lips and onto your teeth. This ultra rich formula makes your lips soft and looks glossy. You can find a Jordana Lipstick for every style, every mood, every occasion or every look. These lipsticks come in .12oz/3.4g. Best Suitable For - All types of lips Tips and Tricks - Apply a little amount of your foundation before applying your lipstick. Foundation even out your lipstick and helps it to last longer. Open your mouth & start from the center of upper & lower lip. Fill in your lipstick on the lips in an outward direction. Blot out the excess oil of your lips with a tissue paper. Made in the United States of America.

Celebrate color with this Maybelline Color Sensational Moisture Extreme Lip Color, a lipstick that has been composed to keep your lips healthy as well as looking gorgeous always. This Velvet Crush adorns your lips with a strong hold color that keeps your lips looking sensual and elegant. This Maybelline implement doubles as a lip balm so you can kick back and relax without worries about dryness and and rough patches on your lips. Velvet Crush Lip Color has a built-in lip balm that ensures to keep your skin enriched with moisture so you can always flaunt luscious lips and a great smile to go with it. The lipstick also is infused with SPF 15, an element that will keep your lips protected from UV rays so you can escape darkening and pigmentation and enjoy only soft and velvety lips that are colored rich and gorgeous. Directions for Use Start applying from the centre of your lip to the outside corners. Smudge color on both lips for better finish. Line the contours of your lips with a lip liner.

You don’t have to worry about fine lines and dry skin showing up by applying lip balm before as the built-in balm fills all those ridges and lines and keeps your pout looking full and luscious. The moisture lasts through the day and so does the color so you are spared from frequent touch-ups. Your lips get a smooth, matte finish that suits any occasion, formal or informal. This Purple Diamond – 130 shade is a deep shade that complements women with dark skin tones and adds a dramatic touch to women with lighter skin tones. Skin damage due to sun exposure is minimised after applying this Color Sensational Lip Color as it is enriched with sunscreens. Give your lips the centre-stage status that they truly deserve. Directions for Use Starting with the centre work towards the outer edges.
